{
  "stem": "4284.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, my father died more or less by falling asleep type of thing, so there was no suffering.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was not ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He just gave out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother and I, of course, were totally confused by this unexpected-- although you can expect it if somebody is ailing, but when you see somebody just simply wither away, and we didn't look much different than my father, you think in a very short time thereafter whether you have the same fate.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- if you want to say the traumatic thing about my father's passing was the burial.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no burial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The corpses were placed outside wherever you lived, onto the street, and a wagon came by in the morning collecting the corpses that had died during the night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you saw heaps of bodies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You were in a confined area that did have a cemetery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as it turned out-- and I'll tell you in a moment-- that one on my survival possibilities was to work on the cemetery at one time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The idea was that you had no formal burial.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They just simply took the body, wrapped it in something like a sheath of material which was much too expensive, so it was the same sheet that's like cheesecloth, very transparent.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The body hung.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The arms flung out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a pit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And your whole ceremony of burial was that you walk to the pit and they just simply turned the sheet around and the body falls in with the others that had just gone through the same burial service--",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You said your own things, what you felt in your heart was all the service.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no service of any kind.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
